0.name: On another plane...
desc: "   You are standing on a strange, organic surface in the middle of a giant
mushroom patch.  The mushrooms are purple in colour and tower all around.
They look to steep to climb, but something about the surface indicates that
they appear to be very supple... Almost as if you could 'go push' your way
into the centre of them.  Maybe.  The sky is a nasty vomit yellow colour.
There is no wind, and no smell.  Somewhere, away to the north, something
so big it casts shadows where no shadows should be, moves with all the grace
of an elf in a tree.  You're not sure you want to be here.

8.name: The centre of a mushroom...
desc: "   You are standing in the centre of a massive mushroom.  The fronds that
parted so nicely to let you in have closed in around you.  There is no
way out now!!  With a sense of dread you realise that your air supply has
been cut off, and very shortly you will run out of air and die!  What are
you going to do now??
